The '''Exultation''' was the term for a biological feature of the male [[t'landa Til]] used to attract female mates. It was created by deep vibrations thrummed by the males' throats and a pseudo-telepathic projection of ecstasy and extreme pleasure. To beings other than t'landa Til, the effect was addictive. This ability was used by [[Teroenza]] and other priests, such as [[Veratil]], by the [[Besadii/Legends|Besadii]] [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]] clan to lure "religious pilgrims" to [[Ylesia/Legends|Ylesia]] where they would be forced to work in [[Spice/Legends|spice]] refineries. By receiving the Exultation each night, the slaves were kept from leaving Ylesia by their own choice. The scam of the Exultation was uncovered by [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and first revealed to [[Bria Tharen]], who, upon leaving Ylesia, took years to overcome her addiction. Once she joined the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], Bria focused her efforts on rescuing slaves from Ylesia and helped develop an effective cure for its addictiveness.

